    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Would you look at that! The real part of the function is the same infinite series as that of <em>cos x</em> and the imaginary part is the same infinite series as that of <em>sin x</em>. That’s it, we’ve done it!</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
